1️⃣ User Experience / Frontend Improvements

Product detail modal/page:
Clicking on a product image opens a detailed view with:

Full description, images carousel, price, category, stock availability.

Reviews and ratings section (already mostly done).

Add-to-cart and Buy buttons right there.

Filter & Sorting options:
For recommendations or latest products:

Sort by price, rating, newest, popularity.

Filter by category, price range, rating, etc.

Pagination / Infinite scroll:
If you have a lot of products, don’t show them all at once. Load in pages or lazy-load as the user scrolls.

Hover effects / UI polish:
Slight animations, hover effects on product cards, buttons changing color, image zoom on hover, etc.

2️⃣ Reviews & Ratings Enhancements

Show average rating & number of reviews on each product card.

Star rating component improvements:

Make stars clickable so users can rate directly on the card.

Review sorting/filtering:

Most helpful, most recent, highest/lowest rating.

User avatars or names:

Show who wrote the review (fake or real usernames).

3️⃣ Recommendation System Improvements

Dynamic recommendations:

Show “People who bought this also bought…” or “Similar trending products”.

Personalized recommendations:

If you implement user accounts, track their history and recommend based on their activity.

Recommendation explanations:

Show why a product was recommended (e.g., “Similar color/style” or “Based on your recent searches”).

4️⃣ Cart & Checkout Enhancements

Cart page:

View all added products, adjust quantity, remove items, see total.

Persistent cart:

Store cart in localStorage or user account.

Buy button integration:

Redirects to a checkout page with payment (can be mocked initially).

5️⃣ Backend Improvements

Search API enhancements:

Full-text search or fuzzy search for product names and descriptions.

Caching & performance:

Cache recommendations for repeated queries for faster response.

Product metadata:

Stock availability, SKU, multiple images, categories, brand.

User authentication:

Register/login to store reviews, cart, and personal recommendations.

6️⃣ Analytics & Logging

Track what products are clicked, viewed, or purchased.

Track which recommendations are actually clicked (to improve algorithm later).

7️⃣ Optional Fun Features

Wishlist / Favorites

Users can save products for later.

Recently viewed products

Carousel showing products the user has looked at.

Product comparison feature

Compare 2–3 products side by side.

Dark mode toggle

Nice-to-have for UI polish.